{"data":[{"name":"80:1","price":"He frowned and turned away,","arabic":"عَبَسَ وَتَوَلَّىٰٓ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5759,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:2","price":"when the blind man came to him[1].","arabic":"أَن جَآءَهُ ٱلۡأَعۡمَىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5760,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1] Abdullah ibn Um Maktūm, an early Muslim who was blind, came to the Prophet (ﷺ) seeking to learn, while the Prophet (ﷺ) was in the middle of a discussion with a leading pagan of Makkah, calling him to Islam. Abdullah was so impatient that he interrupted their discussion. The Prophet (ﷺ) frowned and turned his attention to that pagan. So this Makkan surah was revealed, telling the Prophet (ﷺ) that the faithful blind man was more worthy of attention than that disbeliever.","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:3","price":"How would you know? Perhaps he might be purified[2],","arabic":"وَمَا يُدۡرِيكَ لَعَلَّهُۥ يَزَّكَّىٰٓ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5761,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[2] Through the knowledge he learns from you.","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:4","price":"or he might take heed and benefit from the reminder?","arabic":"أَوۡ يَذَّكَّرُ فَتَنفَعَهُ ٱلذِّكۡرَىٰٓ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5762,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:5","price":"But he who was indifferent[3],","arabic":"أَمَّا مَنِ ٱسۡتَغۡنَىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5763,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[3] Towards faith. Here it is referring to that influential pagan of the Quraysh whom the Prophet (ﷺ) had hoped to embrace Islam.","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:6","price":"you give him your full attention,","arabic":"فَأَنتَ لَهُۥ تَصَدَّىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5764,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:7","price":"although you are not to be blamed if he does not purify himself[4].","arabic":"وَمَا عَلَيۡكَ أَلَّا يَزَّكَّىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5765,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[4] The Prophets are only responsible to convey the message, not for people’s guidance.","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:8","price":"But as for the one who came to you striving [for purification],","arabic":"وَأَمَّا مَن جَآءَكَ يَسۡعَىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5766,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:9","price":"and he fears Allah,","arabic":"وَهُوَ يَخۡشَىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5767,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:10","price":"you let yourself be distracted from him.","arabic":"فَأَنتَ عَنۡهُ تَلَهَّىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5768,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:11","price":"No indeed; this is a reminder –","arabic":"كَلَّآ إِنَّهَا تَذۡكِرَةٞ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5769,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:12","price":"so whoever wills may give heed to it –","arabic":"فَمَن شَآءَ ذَكَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5770,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:13","price":"on venerable pages,","arabic":"فِي صُحُفٖ مُّكَرَّمَةٖ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5771,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:14","price":"exalted and purified,","arabic":"مَّرۡفُوعَةٖ مُّطَهَّرَةِۭ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5772,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:15","price":"[preserved] in the hands of angel-scribes,","arabic":"بِأَيۡدِي سَفَرَةٖ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5773,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:16","price":"honorable and obedient.","arabic":"كِرَامِۭ بَرَرَةٖ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5774,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:17","price":"Woe to man; how ungrateful he is[5]!","arabic":"قُتِلَ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ مَآ أَكۡفَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5775,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[5] i.e., the disbelievers.","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:18","price":"From what did He create him?","arabic":"مِنۡ أَيِّ شَيۡءٍ خَلَقَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5776,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:19","price":"He created him from a drop of semen and proportioned him[6],","arabic":"مِن نُّطۡفَةٍ خَلَقَهُۥ فَقَدَّرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5777,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[6] His creation, provisions, life span, etc.","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:20","price":"then He made the way easy for him[7];","arabic":"ثُمَّ ٱلسَّبِيلَ يَسَّرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5778,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[7] i.e., the way out of his mothers’ wombs (his birth), or the way to guidance.","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:21","price":"then He caused him to die and be buried;","arabic":"ثُمَّ أَمَاتَهُۥ فَأَقۡبَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5779,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:22","price":"then when He wills, He will resurrect him.","arabic":"ثُمَّ إِذَا شَآءَ أَنشَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5780,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:23","price":"Yet he has not fulfilled what He commanded him.","arabic":"كَلَّا لَمَّا يَقۡضِ مَآ أَمَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5781,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:24","price":"Let man consider the food he eats:","arabic":"فَلۡيَنظُرِ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ إِلَىٰ طَعَامِهِۦٓ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5782,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:25","price":"How We pour down rainwater in torrents,","arabic":"أَنَّا صَبَبۡنَا ٱلۡمَآءَ صَبّٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5783,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:26","price":"and cause the soil to split open [for sprouts],","arabic":"ثُمَّ شَقَقۡنَا ٱلۡأَرۡضَ شَقّٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5784,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:27","price":"and cause grains to grow in it,","arabic":"فَأَنۢبَتۡنَا فِيهَا حَبّٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5785,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:28","price":"as well as grapes and fodder,","arabic":"وَعِنَبٗا وَقَضۡبٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5786,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:29","price":"and olive trees and date palms,","arabic":"وَزَيۡتُونٗا وَنَخۡلٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5787,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:30","price":"and dense orchards,","arabic":"وَحَدَآئِقَ غُلۡبٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5788,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:31","price":"and fruits and grass,","arabic":"وَفَٰكِهَةٗ وَأَبّٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5789,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:32","price":"as provision for you and your livestock.","arabic":"مَّتَٰعٗا لَّكُمۡ وَلِأَنۡعَٰمِكُمۡ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5790,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:33","price":"But when the Deafening Blast[8] comes,","arabic":"فَإِذَا جَآءَتِ ٱلصَّآخَّةُ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5791,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[8] The piercing Blast; the second Blast for resurrection.","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:34","price":"on that Day everyone will flee from his brother,","arabic":"يَوۡمَ يَفِرُّ ٱلۡمَرۡءُ مِنۡ أَخِيهِ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5792,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:35","price":"and from his mother and father,","arabic":"وَأُمِّهِۦ وَأَبِيهِ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5793,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:36","price":"and from his wife and children.","arabic":"وَصَٰحِبَتِهِۦ وَبَنِيهِ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5794,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:37","price":"On that day, everyone will have enough concern of his own[9].","arabic":"لِكُلِّ ٱمۡرِيٕٖ مِّنۡهُمۡ يَوۡمَئِذٖ شَأۡنٞ يُغۡنِيهِ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5795,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[9] Thus forgetting all others.","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:38","price":"On that Day, some faces will be bright,","arabic":"وُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ مُّسۡفِرَةٞ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5796,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:39","price":"cheerful and rejoicing;","arabic":"ضَاحِكَةٞ مُّسۡتَبۡشِرَةٞ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5797,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:40","price":"while other faces will be dust-stained,","arabic":"وَوُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٍ عَلَيۡهَا غَبَرَةٞ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5798,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:41","price":"covered in darkness.","arabic":"تَرۡهَقُهَا قَتَرَةٌ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5799,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"80:42","price":"Such are the disbelievers, the wicked.","arabic":"أُوْلَٰٓئِكَ هُمُ ٱلۡكَفَرَةُ ٱلۡفَجَرَةُ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5800,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"}],"chapter":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa","Chapter Abasa","Surah 80","Chapter 80","He Frowned","عبس"]}